            "often struggle with accurately",
            "reconstructing document structure,",
            "leading to \u0027structural hallucinations\u0027.",
            "These hallucinations can manifest as",
            "disordered table rows, fabricated",
            "formulas, and incorrect syntax within",
            "documents.",
            "FireRed-OCR-2B is designed to improve",
            "parsing accuracy, particularly for",
            "tables and LaTeX documents.",
            "Traditional document digitization",
            "involves layout detection, text",
            "extraction, and structural",
            "reconstruction, a process prone to",
            "errors."
          ]
